Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.90,0:02:17.45,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}超越吧超越那无数风浪 向明日抗争的你 请替我守护
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.46,0:02:20.15,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}my life I trade in for your pain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.19,0:02:25.04,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}莫再回首 振翅去飞
